# Uploads directory

This directory stores uploaded files when using local storage instead of S3.

## Structure

- Screenshots from transaction submissions
- Evidence files uploaded by agents
- Other user-uploaded files

## Security

- Only image files (PNG, JPG, JPEG) are allowed
- Maximum file size: 8MB
- Files are served with appropriate MIME types
- Access is controlled by authentication middleware

## Configuration

Set `LOCAL_UPLOAD_PATH` environment variable to change the upload directory.
Default: `./uploads`
